1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 18=

4
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:15,599
Lu!

5
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,319
Get away!

6
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,239
Don't touch me!

7
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:20,480
If not for you,

8
00:01:20,959 --> 00:01:24,040
how would I have ended up
beaten half to death by Duke Zhen's men?

9
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,040
Lu,

10
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:27,079
what are you saying?

11
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,719
Everything I did was for your sake.

12
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:31,959
Who could've known
things would go wrong?

13
00:01:33,319 --> 00:01:34,200
Don't worry.

14
00:01:34,210 --> 00:01:35,470
I'm already thinking of a solution.

15
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,799
I can still help you.

16
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:38,680
And you still dare toy with me?

17
00:01:39,879 --> 00:01:42,239
You and Shen Zhinian,

18
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:43,840
you venomous sisters,

19
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,079
joined forces to ruin me.

20
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,879
What nonsense are you talking about?

21
00:01:46,879 --> 00:01:48,640
How could I possibly
join forces with her?

22
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:52,519
I wish she would die in the palace.

23
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:53,799
Fine.

24
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,439
Then answer me this.

25
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:59,560
Why was Jinsong Pavilion a trap?

26
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:02,760
Why was Nangong Xuanyu
there waiting for prey?

27
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,760
Impossible.

28
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:06,000
In my previous life,

29
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,960
someone bought the puzzle box there

30
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,360
and was later favored by him.

31
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,199
In previous life?

32
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,039
Lu, your medicine has gone cold.

33
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,479
I... I'll go

34
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:20,400
prepare another bowl.

35
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:22,080
Nanqiao,

36
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:34,120
without explaining things clearly,

37
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,360
you think you can run away?

38
00:02:58,479 --> 00:02:59,240
Lu,

39
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,479
what are you doing?

40
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:01,840
Let go of me.

41
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,039
Shen Nanqiao,

42
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,759
I've never understood

43
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:14,680
why you used to act so superior,

44
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:18,080
mocking and belittling me

45
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,840
every time you saw me.

46
00:03:20,919 --> 00:03:24,599
Then one day, you suddenly insisted on
marrying me at all costs.

47
00:03:25,479 --> 00:03:26,520
You even

48
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,840
resorted to schemes against me.

49
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:06,520
You deserve to die.

50
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,560
You deserve to die!

51
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,439
- You ruined my entire life!
- Lu!

52
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,639
I have a way!

53
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:13,199
I still have a way!

54
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:14,960
I really do!

55
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,519
Please don't kill me.

56
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,160
That foolish woman ruined me.

57
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:31,759
That foolish woman ruined me!

58
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,720
They all harmed me.

59
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:47,519
They all looked down on me!

60
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:51,439
But I'm not afraid.

61
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:56,800
My ancestors once held
the highest official rank.

62
00:04:57,319 --> 00:05:01,000
Noble blood flows through me!

63
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:04,160
I will definitely

64
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,600
become the admired heir

65
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:09,800
of the Lu family once again,

66
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:15,600
and restore the Lu family's
century old glory in Chizhou!

67
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:25,399
Young Lady, something happened
to Shen Nanqiao.

68
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,439
What happened?

69
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:27,959
Shen Nanqiao and Young Master Lu

70
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,590
were struck to death
by lightning last night.

71
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,319
Their bodies were burned black.

72
00:05:32,079 --> 00:05:33,079
How could that happen?

73
00:05:35,620 --> 00:05:40,780
(Shen Residence)

74
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:48,759
If lightning truly
struck them down here,

75
00:05:48,900 --> 00:05:50,639
then why are
all the plants in this courtyard

76
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:52,120
completely unharmed?

77
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:54,040
There's not even a trace of scorching.

78
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,040
The coroner's report says

79
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:03,800
their bodies were lying right here.

80
00:06:04,199 --> 00:06:06,000
Then what explains

81
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,800
these drag marks?

82
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:09,079
Miss Nanqiao!

83
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,040
Miss Nanqiao!

84
00:06:13,050 --> 00:06:13,990
Something terrible has happened!

85
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:14,959
Master is in trouble!

86
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:15,920
What happened?

87
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,270
Why are you here, Miss Zhinian?

88
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,800
Miss Nanqiao, she...

89
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,560
Where is she?

90
00:06:24,279 --> 00:06:25,240
What happened?

91
00:06:25,439 --> 00:06:26,199
Tell me first.

92
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,439
Master and Madam

93
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,800
were on their way to the capital
to visit Miss Nanqiao.

94
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,120
But

95
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:34,160
on the way,

96
00:06:34,170 --> 00:06:36,930
they received a letter telling them
to change course to Mount Nanhua.

97
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:39,160
But after entering the mountain,
they vanished.

98
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:40,319
Vanished?

99
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,879
Mount Nanhua again?

100
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:45,759
Shen Zhinian.

101
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:50,390
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Your Majesty.

102
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:51,759
Rise.

103
00:06:52,290 --> 00:06:52,879
Your Majesty.

104
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,399
Mm.

105
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:54,279
This is for you.

106
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,439
What is it?

107
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:58,399
Wen Ling said sweets

108
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,839
can cheer people up.

109
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,040
You don't actually think

110
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,720
I'm upset over Lu Jianglin's death,

111
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,720
do you?

112
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:11,720
Wen Ling said the first person
someone loves in their youth

113
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,600
is always different.

114
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,199
Don't worry.

115
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:15,199
I won't mind it.

116
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:17,279
He's dead now.

117
00:07:17,420 --> 00:07:19,780
This is the last piece of candy
you'll ever eat for him.

118
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,519
(No way.)

119
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,319
(Is he trying to cheer me up?)

120
00:07:33,519 --> 00:07:34,879
Once you've eaten my candy,

121
00:07:34,900 --> 00:07:36,990
you're not allowed to be sad
over another man anymore.

122
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,399
Wen Ling taught you that too?

123
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,639
How does he know so much?

124
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:44,160
Does he have many wives and concubines?

125
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,000
He looks

126
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,560
quite honest and dependable though.

127
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,000
He's not honest.

128
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,279
He's quite the charmer.

129
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:05,279
These marks look like something
was dragged across the ground.

130
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:09,560
Mm.

131
00:08:09,759 --> 00:08:11,199
I think so too.

132
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:14,240
Shen Nanqiao and Lu Jianglin

133
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,839
died under very suspicious circumstances.

134
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,560
And this elderly man
escaped to the capital to report

135
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:20,439
that my father and legal mother

136
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,680
also disappeared at Mount Nanhua.

137
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,040
(Again, Mount Nanhua.)

138
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,319
It's getting late.

139
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:30,720
Bring him back
to the palace for questioning first.

140
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:32,360
Come back with me.

141
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:33,360
Tomorrow morning,

142
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:34,519
we'll go visit Jiang Chen.

143
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,080
What happened to Lord Jiang?

144
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:36,840
He's ill.

145
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:39,240
He never used to take leave before.

146
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,679
But this time,

147
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:41,879
he requested seven whole days.

148
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:44,039
Is his illness really that serious?

149
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:48,519
Lord Jiang has always treated me well.

150
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:50,559
I should go visit him.

151
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:52,120
Lord Jiang?

152
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,360
You say it quite naturally.

153
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:57,120
He's a peerless noble gentleman.

154
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,559
And besides, he is Lord Jiang.

155
00:08:58,559 --> 00:09:00,600
There's nothing wrong
with me calling him that.

156
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:02,200
He's a noble gentleman?

157
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,840
I'm the Son of Heaven.

158
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,639
"Peerless noble gentleman"?

159
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,710
Why don't you ever describe me like that?

160
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,480
I wasn't the one who wanted to go.

161
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:13,840
Then I simply won't go.

162
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:15,399
I'm ordering you to come with me.

163
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,240
I'm not going.

164
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:16,919
You must.

165
00:09:16,930 --> 00:09:17,480
I'm not going.

166
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:24,879
(Jiang Residence)

167
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:27,120
Lord Jiang doesn't live
at Duke Zhen's Manor?

168
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:30,200
After Duke Zhen's first wife died,

169
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,799
he took sixteen concubines.

170
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:33,759
So after Jiang Chen

171
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,519
came of age at eighteen,

172
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:36,970
he established his own residence

173
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:38,799
and rarely returned there.

174
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,759
The women in the palace all say

175
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:44,360
that Lord Jiang is as refined as jade

176
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,620
and as steadfast as a pine tree.

177
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:47,679
The most captivating man in Daliang.

178
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,320
Shen Zhinian,

179
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:55,600
do you really think
a death-exemption medal

180
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:56,879
can save your life?

181
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:58,960
You actually dare say such things to me?

182
00:09:59,919 --> 00:10:01,039
Your Majesty sees all.

183
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:02,200
I'm not like

184
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,200
other women.

185
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,559
When I choose a man,
not only must he be handsome,

186
00:10:05,559 --> 00:10:07,320
he must also be the most capable,

187
00:10:07,330 --> 00:10:08,190
the most broad minded,

188
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,320
the most competent,

189
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,799
and the most manly.

190
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,519
Don't think a few compliments

191
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:15,240
mean I won't punish you.

192
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,610
It's because I'm magnanimous

193
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,919
that I let it slide.

194
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,000
Your Majesty has great power,

195
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,840
great authority,

196
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,960
and lives in a grand palace.

197
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,800
Everything about
Your Majesty is great except

198
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,480
your tolerance.

199
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,039
Shen Zhinian,

200
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,990
ever since receiving
that death-exemption medal,

201
00:10:31,639 --> 00:10:33,120
you've become even bolder.

202
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,879
Your Majesty.

203
00:10:38,039 --> 00:10:38,639
Your Majesty.

204
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,559
Lady Shen.

205
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:43,360
I heard you were ill,
so I came to visit you.

206
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:44,919
I'm not sick.

207
00:10:45,399 --> 00:10:46,759
I just didn't want to attend court

208
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:48,159
and wanted to sleep in for a day.

209
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:49,799
Then let's sleep together.

210
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,799
Your Majesty.

211
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:43,159
Your Majesty.

212
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,720
This is completely improper.

213
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:46,679
If the old ministers found out,

214
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:48,090
they'd criticize Your Majesty again.

215
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,320
Then how about we don't lie down?

216
00:11:53,159 --> 00:11:54,320
Would you like to play chess?

217
00:11:55,519 --> 00:11:56,120
No.

218
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,720
Otherwise Your Majesty
will mock me again.

219
00:11:59,759 --> 00:12:00,600
Then...

220
00:12:01,559 --> 00:12:03,919
Go cook something for us.

221
00:12:05,159 --> 00:12:06,639
Your Majesty is truly cruel.

222
00:12:06,799 --> 00:12:08,400
It's bad enough you won't let me sleep,

223
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,790
now you're ordering me to cook too.

224
00:12:11,279 --> 00:12:13,159
The last time I ate your cooking

225
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,559
was seven years ago.

226
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:16,360
Now,

227
00:12:16,559 --> 00:12:18,080
you are the refined as jade,

228
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,279
steadfast as pine,

229
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:21,320
number one handsome man in Daliang.

230
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:22,679
Naturally,

231
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:24,159
I can no longer eat food made by you.

232
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:30,399
Your Majesty's mouth is truly unbearable.

233
00:12:32,799 --> 00:12:33,639
Jiang Chen,

234
00:12:33,919 --> 00:12:35,120
I'm taking away your title

235
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,879
as Daliang's most captivating man.

236
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:44,480
Lord Jiang was chased away by you.

237
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,360
(Zhinian,)

238
00:12:54,679 --> 00:12:56,840
(with you by my side from now on,)

239
00:12:57,519 --> 00:12:59,559
(my life will finally feel complete.)

240
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:08,620
♪Dim lamps, concerns unheard by anyone♪

241
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:11,440
But you deserve punishment too.

242
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:14,520
You heard someone insulting me
and still didn't defend me.

243
00:13:14,799 --> 00:13:16,679
How would I dare interrupt?

244
00:13:16,679 --> 00:13:19,820
♪Faint rouge hides
the tenderness in the eyes♪

245
00:13:19,820 --> 00:13:23,220
♪Every step is treacherous,
regardless of the world♪

246
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:39,000
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

247
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:45,960
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

248
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:49,960
♪If we don't meet♪

249
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:53,400
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

250
00:13:53,600 --> 00:14:00,120
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

251
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:06,920
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

252
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:13,600
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

253
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:20,800
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

254
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:27,680
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

255
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:33,800
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

256
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:41,320
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

257
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:48,160
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

258
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:54,880
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

